Total production, productivity, recovered paper utilization, and per capita production

Dataset containing industrial wood and roundwood statistics, productivity, recovered paper utilization rate and per capita indudustrial wood production.

pt_pu

Format

A data frame with 151 observations of 15 variables:

Years
Years
Total.Industrial.Wood.Product.Production
Industrial wood production in thousand tons
Roundwood.Equivalents.of.Production.Hardwoods
Hardwood production in million ft<sup>3</sup>
Roundwood.Equivalents.of.Production.Softwoods
Softwood production in million ft<sup>3</sup>
Roundwood.Equivalents.of.Production.Totals.millionftcubed
Production totals in million ft<sup>3</sup>
Roundwood.Equivalents.of.Production.Totals.thousand.short.tons
Production totals in thousand short tons
Roundwood.Equivalents.of.Production.Totals.thousand.metric.tons
Production totals in thousand metric tons
Industrial.Wood.Productivity.lbs.ftsquared
Industrial wood product output per unit of roundwood input in (lbs/ft3)
Industrial.Wood.Productivity
Industrial wood product output per unit of roundwood input in tons/tons
Recovered.Paper.Utilization.Rate(AF&PA)
Recovered paper utilization rate
U.S.Population
United States population in millions
Per.Capita.Industrial.Wood.Product.Production
Per capita industrial wood product production, lbs/capita
HW.Agrifiber
Hardwood Agrifiber (units?)
HW.Roundwood
Hardwood Roundwood (units?)
U.S.Timber.Harvest
United States Timber Harvest
Misc
This is unnamed column in Ince_Table3
